dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Waterman Mountain quadrangle, Los Angeles County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle WATERMAN MTN., CA 1959, 34117-C8-TF-024. Photo inspected 1972".
"Prepared in cooperation with the Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History and the Angeles National Forest".
Includes 1 col. cross section, quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
